EntityExtractorFactory
public class ResponseObjectEntityExtractorFactory
extends DefaultEntityExtractorFactory

This class represents the method level creation of a "rich response object" that has the @ResponseObject annotation. These EntityExtractors will be used to implment methods of ResponseObject via ResponseObjectEntityExtractor
